<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Supervisor Selection Confirmation - COMSATS Internship Portal</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Reset styles */
        body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        table, td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }
        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            border: 0;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            background-color: #f8fafc !important;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif !important;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            width: 200px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            color: #059669;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .logo-subtitle {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #d1fae5;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .celebration-icon {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .celebration-circle {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .supervisor-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
            border: 2px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .supervisor-card h3 {
            color: #059669;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .supervisor-info {
            color: #065f46;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .next-steps ul {
            color: #1e40af;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .next-steps li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-text">COMSATS</div>
                <div class="logo-subtitle">UNIVERSITY</div>
            </div>
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
            <p>Your Supervisor Request Has Been Accepted</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Celebration Icon -->
            <div class="celebration-icon">
                <div class="celebration-circle">ðŸŽ‰</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="greeting">
                Excellent News, {{studentName}}!
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We're thrilled to inform you that your supervision request has been <strong>accepted</strong>! 
                {{supervisorName}} has agreed to be your academic supervisor for your internship journey.
            </div>
            
            <!-- Supervisor Details Card -->
            <div class="supervisor-card">
                <h3>Your Assigned Supervisor</h3>
                <div class="supervisor-info"><strong>Name:</strong> {{supervisorName}}</div>
                <div class="supervisor-info"><strong>Department:</strong> {{supervisorDepartment}}</div>
                <div class="supervisor-info"><strong>Email:</strong> {{supervisorEmail}}</div>
                {{#if supervisorPhone}}
                <div class="supervisor-info"><strong>Phone:</strong> {{supervisorPhone}}</div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="supervisor-info"><strong>Office:</strong> {{supervisorOffice}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                This is an important milestone in your academic journey! Your supervisor will guide you through 
                the internship process, help you with job applications, and provide valuable mentorship.
            </div>
            
            <!-- Next Steps -->
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What's Next?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Contact Your Supervisor:</strong> Reach out to introduce yourself and discuss your goals</li>
                    <li><strong>Schedule a Meeting:</strong> Arrange your first supervision meeting</li>
                    <li><strong>Job Applications:</strong> You can now start applying for internship positions</li>
                    <li><strong>Regular Check-ins:</strong> Maintain regular communication with your supervisor</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Your Portal</a>
            </div>
            
            <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
            
            
            <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                Best wishes for your internship journey!<br>
                <strong>COMSATS Internship Portal Team</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>COMSATS Internship Portal</strong></p>
            <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>For support, contact your supervisor or the internship coordinator.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                Â© 2025 COMSATS University. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>